data.description: A REWARDING ESCAPE PEACEFULLY SITUATED! This Custom Built 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom 2,984 sq. ft. updated Expanded Ranch sits on a 1 acre corner lot in the desirable Roosevelt City area. Loaded with character, this property has a unique architectural style and design making it stand out from the rest. Richly-appointed spaces include large gathering areas. Vaulted ceilings, custom crown molding with warm mood lighting, 6-panel wood doors in the main living spaces, hardwood floors throughout, and an oversized great room with an 18f ft. wet bar, a wood burning fireplace, and surround sound system. Formal Dining room and an eat-in kitchen with high grade appliances. All this plus an additional 2,100 sq. ft. of living space in the finished basement. Enter through the circular driveway where you will be presented with a spray fountain surrounded by pristine landscape and two-car garage. Access the expansive fenced-in backyard from the great room onto the wraparound deck. A private escape of verdant surroundings with a large storage space fully finished; perfect for the car or craftsman enthusiast. This unique HOME is a MUST see! Schedule a tour today.
